2004-06-18 00:03  kelnos

	* settings/backdrop_settings.c, settings/settings_common.h,
	  src/xfce-backdrop.c, src/xfce-backdrop.h, src/xfce-desktop.c: add
	  image brightness % option as suggested by some dude in #xfce.
	  it's actually image color saturation, but it's a pretty neat
	  effect.  don't worry, there's no performance impact if you leave
	  it at 100% ^_~

