2004-02-11 21:31  kelnos

	* src/menu.c: i don't know why this broke launching things from the
	  menu for some people, so i'm putting it back until i have a
	  chance to look at it more closely.  unfortunately, this way, if
	  you kill xfdesktop, all apps launched by it will die as well.

