2003-04-05 02:10  xfce

	* src/: backdrop.c, main.c, menu.c, settings.c, workspaces.c:
	  Revert last change in debug.h, use "??" instead of ((__const char
	  *)0) Replace DBG() statements with TRACE() in libxfcegui4 and
	  xfwm4 because it was generating far too much logs in simple debug
	  mode (use --enable-debug=full to get full traces) Add params to
	  TRACE() (just like in DBG()) Remove trailing CR in log messages

