2003-01-18 14:54  xfce

	* ChangeLog: Update ChangeLog

2003-01-18 14:51  xfce

	* src/: backdrop.c, main.c: * Remove double buffering in desktop
	  window otherwise gtk allocates twice the size of the screen in
	  video memory which can show to be unusable even on a GeForce II
	  MX with 32Mb using 3D because the video RAM alloted to pixmaps
	  cannot handle the total amount of pixmaps.  * Reduce scale
	  quality to BILINEAR instead of HYPER because it takes too long
	  even on a PIV 1.7GHz scalling from 1024x768 to 1280x768

